msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Ah!\r\nI finally found you, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "You're... the mascot guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Righto! I'm Ono Michio-kun's\r\nproducer, Hironaka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "I really can't thank you enough for your\r\nperformance as Ono Michio-kun the other day!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Let me guess...\r\nYou want me to do it again?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "You're sharper than you look!\r\nI <font_kind=yakuza_italic>do</font_kind> want that! I do, I do!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Hey! Hold on a sec, please!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "I'm begging you! Michio-kun's popularity has\r\nbeen through the roof since the last event!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "We can't just stop now.\r\nThink about how disappointed your fans would be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "You're not dragging me into this again.\r\nNo way am I doing another talk show."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Oh, you don't need to worry, then.\r\nThat's not what it'll be this time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "It's, drum roll... A concert!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "A concert...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Yup! We've actually been thinking about\r\nproducing an Ono Michio-kun music CD."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "But before we can do that, Ono Michio-kun\r\nwill have to show off his pipes!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Do you like to sing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Uh, I guess it's not so bad..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Perfect! Will you be Ono Michio-kun\r\nfor our concert then? Whaddya say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Go away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Don't be like that!\r\nCan't you make an exception for the children?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "And just think, Michio-kun's rising popularity\r\nwill be great PR for Onomichi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "It'll be a kick in the pants for this sleepy town.\r\nJust what the aging population needs nowadays."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "So won't you help me out? For Onomichi.\r\nI'll reward you handsomely, of course!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Not just for the children, but for the town, too...\r\nI guess I <font_kind=yakuza_italic>do</font_kind> want to give back. What should I do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Sorry, let me think it over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "All right! I'll be waiting for you,\r\nso just let me know when you decide!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Fine, I'll do it.\r\nBut this is the last time, you got it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Anything for my savior!\r\nCome on, let's get you suited up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "That damn costume again...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Mm, a perfect fit! Not that I'm surprised."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "It's still heavy. And hot. And hard to breathe in.\r\nAnyway, where's this concert?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Well... It's right here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Seriously? This is a pretty strange venue."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "There wasn't anywhere better.\r\nYou know how rural Onomichi is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Well, step right in!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "O-Okay..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, please!\r\nBe Michio-kun for our concert!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Hi there! Thanks for letting us perform here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "No, thank <font_kind=yakuza_italic>you</font_kind>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Crap, it's Mama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Oh, is that our Michio-kun?\r\nHe's a <font_kind=yakuza_italic>cutey</font_kind>. Hi there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "I can't let her recognize my voice.\r\nHm, maybe if I change it a bit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "N-Nice to michi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Wow, you sound super manly.\r\nAlmost familiar, somehow..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Probably a coincidence-michi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'm sure.\r\nNobody I know would ever get in that thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "That's right-michi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "I think I fooled her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "All right, Michio-kun!\r\nThe customers are coming, so get in position!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "W-Will do..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "It's great seeing you all at our special\r\nOno Michio-kun concert! Thank you for coming!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Man, I'm pumped!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "I think yer my type, Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Hey, these aren't kids at all.\r\nIt's just a bunch of old men."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "We <font_kind=yakuza_italic>are</font_kind> at a bar. Only adults\r\nare allowed in a place like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "But look! Aren't their smiles\r\njust so innocent and childlike?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Don't try to talk your way out of this.\r\nOld men are old men."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Meh, oh well. Too late now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "The song I want you to sing is called\r\n<font_kind=yakuza_italic>Today is a Diamond</font_kind>. You know it, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "I do..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "As you know, the lyrics are amazing!\r\nYou'll do great! Now, get out there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "I won't forget this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Now then, Michio-kun!\r\nWhat are you singing for us today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Um... Do you know <font_kind=yakuza_italic>Today is a Diamond</font_kind>?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Ooooh, hell yeah! What a pick!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "You've got great taste, Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "I'm pissin' myself with excitement!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Now, it would be a little too boring\r\nif we just had him sing for us normally, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "That's why we'll be using a special rule today!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "For this concert, we'll take advantage\r\nof Joysound's grading feature!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "If Michio-kun gets 80 points or higher...\r\nhe'll be signed for his very own CD debut!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Whoaaaaaa!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Fer real!? That's incredible!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Dudeee!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "No way..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Glad to see you all so excited!\r\nIt's almost time for the main event!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Ono Michio-kun's <font_kind=yakuza_italic>Today is a Diamond</font_kind>!\r\nLet's hear it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "Hey, you did great, Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "Wahoo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "Nice job, Michio! Nice job!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "I got less than 80 points..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Thanks so much! I could really\r\nfeel the raw passion in your voice!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "But... Uh oh!\r\nHe didn't beat the 80 point requirement..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun won't be able to make\r\nhis CD debut with that low of a score."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Huhhhhhh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "What!? Jus' let the guy sing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Boo, boo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Although... Requests are coming in from\r\nall over the country for a Michio-kun CD."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "Okay! As a thank you to our fans,\r\nwe'll go ahead with the CD debut!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "That was great!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Yeah! Yer the best!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "Nice one, Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "Not bad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "What a beautiful voice! Thank you so much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "And since he got over 80 points,\r\nhis CD debut is all but confirmed!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "Wahooooooooo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "He did it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "Amazing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Isn't this great, Michio-kun?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Michio! Michio! Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Michio! Michio! Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Michio! Michio! Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "Your fans really love you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I guess so..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun, you can't leave them hanging.\r\nGive them your trademark introduction!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "Ugh, that again?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Oh well... Here we go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "With my charming hassaku face!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Steamy Onomichi ramen hat!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Cute fish pouch!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Cool boots, vital for any fisherman!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "And my bold and trendy Ono shirt!\r\nThat's right, I'm the pride of Onomichi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Ono..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "Yeahhhhhh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san really has it rough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "I've really gotta thank you for today!\r\nEveryone's so pumped for Michio-kun's debut!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "You probably would've gone ahead with\r\nthe CD no matter what score I got, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "I wonder...\r\nAnyway, here you go! This is your reward!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "Oh, and take this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "Th-This is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "It's a preview of the upcoming Michio-kun CD.\r\nI wanted you to see it before anyone else!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "Soooooo? What do you think?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "Hm... I'm not really sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "Either way, you came through in the clutch there!\r\nI can't wait until next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "No, I'm finished.\r\nThere <font_kind=yakuza_italic>is</font_kind> no \"next time.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "Whattt, really?\r\nBut he's just getting popular!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "People will like him no matter who's inside.\r\nIt doesn't have to be me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "You can't keep forcing me into this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "I'm not here for fun. There's something important\r\nI have to do, and I'm damn well gonna do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "I can't help you anymore, you got that?\r\nYou'll have to move forward on your own."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "I get it. You were just so good, though.\r\nThat's why I kept relying on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "But even with your skill,\r\nI shouldn't have pressured you so much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "...I understand.\r\nI won't trouble you anymore, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "I'll do whatever it takes to make Michio-kun\r\nthe most popular mascot around!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "You'll come crawling back asking\r\nto get inside that costume again, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "That's the spirit. I can't wait."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "Oh... And take care of Michio."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "I will!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Thank you so much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "No, that's not right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "Thank you so michi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "You're welcome-michi."
msgstr ""

